item.title: Use F Minor or B Minor for a Future Bass song?
item.dc:creator: akabillposters
item.description:
I never have, but probably should.
(Still hoping they’ll add support for Chromatic as a persistent default in the next update. Still don’t understand why they haven’t already, but hey…)

Even if you’re in Chromatic (my first action on any new project, hence why ^^^^^), the Key is still used for tuning drums. My low-end can sometimes get a bit muddy, so I should be paying more attention to the Key setting if I’m using Auxy drums - especially as I tend to stack/layer drums.
